text: Eleanor May Tomlinson (born 19 May 1992) is an English actress. She has appeared in movies. In 2013, she played Princess Isabelle in Jack the Giant Slayer. She later acted in the movies Love Wedding Repeat (2020) and Colette (2018). In The White Queen, Tomlinson played Lady Isabel Neville. Tomlinson was born in London, England. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:English television actors Category:English movie actors Category:Actors from London Category:Living people
